        "item-1": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "expand_by_default": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "How do I make a purchase?",
            "text": "<p>You can shop with LE FIGUE online or in person at our retail locations. We accept a variety of major credit cards and approved payment methods at checkout.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item-2": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "expand_by_default": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "How do I know if my order is confirmed?",
            "text": "<p>Once your order has been placed, you will receive an order confirmation by email with your order details. Please review the confirmation carefully and contact us as soon as possible if anything needs to be updated.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item-3": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "expand_by_default": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "Can I change my shipping address after my order is placed?",
            "text": "<p>If your order was placed through Shop, you may be able to update your shipping details directly after placing the order.</p><p>If your order was placed through another payment method or checkout tool, please email us at <a href=\"mailto:care@lefigue.com\" target=\"_blank\">care@lefigue.com</a> with your order number and the updated shipping address. We will do our best to assist before the order is shipped.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item-4": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "expand_by_default": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "Can I change my billing address after placing my order?",
            "text": "<p>For security reasons, billing details may not always be editable after an order has been placed. If you notice an issue with your billing information, please email<a href=\"mailto:care@lefigue.com\" target=\"_blank\">care@lefigue.com</a>with your order number as soon as possible, and our team will help review the order.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_YVepTt": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "expand_by_default": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "What payment methods do you accept?",
            "text": "<p>We accept major credit cards and selected digital payment options online and in store. Available payment methods may vary depending on the checkout method used.</p>"
          }
        }
