          "settings": {
            "expand_by_default": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "What size should I order?",
            "text": "<p>If you visit us in store, our team will be happy to assist with sizing.</p><p>For online orders, please refer to the size guide provided on the product page. If you are unsure, you may contact us before placing your order and we will do our best to help you select the right size.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item-2": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "expand_by_default": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "Where can I find information on sustainability?",
            "text": "<p>LE FIGUE works with a curated selection of designers, and sustainability practices may vary by designer and collection.</p><p>Depending on the piece, some of our partner designers may use materials such as lab-grown diamonds, recycled gold, recycled silver, or responsibly sourced materials. When available, these details will be included on the product page or shared by our team upon request.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item-3": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "expand_by_default": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "Do you offer gift cards?",
            "text": "<p>Yes. LE FIGUE gift cards are available for purchase online and in store.</p><p>Gift cards may be used toward eligible purchases online or in person, depending on the checkout method and gift card format. Gift cards are non-refundable and cannot be exchanged for cash.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_NLmdgj": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "expand_by_default": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "How should I care for my jewelry?",
            "text": "<p>To preserve the quality of your jewelry, we recommend keeping each piece away from water, perfume, lotion, chemicals, and excessive humidity. Store your jewelry separately in a pouch or jewelry box when not in use.</p><p>For delicate, plated, pearl, gemstone, or handmade pieces, extra care is recommended. Please refer to any care instructions included with your piece or contact our team for guidance.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_3xjgMT": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "expand_by_default": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "Are all pieces available online and in store?",
            "text": "<p>Product availability may vary between online and in-store locations. Some pieces may be exclusive to a specific store, designer edit, appointment, or limited release.</p><p>If you are looking for a specific item, please contact <a href=\"mailto:care@lefigue.com\" target=\"_blank\">care@lefigue.com</a> and our team can help check availability.</p>"
          }
        }
